No. D-2546. In the Matter of Discipline of Samuel Regester Neel, III. 562 U.S. 815, 131 S. Ct. 406,

178 L. Ed. 2d 271,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7508. October 4, 2010.

Samuel Regester Neel, III, of Tallahassee, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
